      "validation_source": "oahudiveguide.com,loveoahu.org,atlasobscura.com",
      "last_qa_date": "2026-06-06",
      "description": "Leeward shore dive at Hawaii Electric Co. discharge pipes. Warm water effluent attracts marine life. Average depth 20-30 ft near discharge. Very strong currents near pipe discharge—not suitable for true beginners. Sea turtles, spotted eagle rays, spinner dolphins (occasional), white-tip reef sharks, eels, octopus."
    }
